io.confluent.ksql.rest.server.execution

Enum CustomExecutors

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CustomExecutors>
      • io.confluent.ksql.rest.server.execution.CustomExecutors
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CustomExecutors>

    public enum CustomExecutors
extends java.lang.Enum<CustomExecutors>
    A suite of StatementExecutors that do not need to be distributed. Each handles a corresponding Class<? extends Statement> and is assumed that the ConfiguredStatement that is passed in matches the expected class.
